OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The first memorial to remember the     
OL,6, victims of the Battersea Park funfair  
OL,7, disaster has been unveiled.            
OL,9,FFive children were killed and 13 others
OL,10,Finjured when the fair's rollercoaster  
OL,11,Fcame off its tracks on 30 May 1972.    
OL,13,FA tree was planted on Monday to        
OL,14,Fcommemorate the disaster's 50th        
OL,15,Fanniversary, while plans are also being
OL,16,Fput in place for a permanent memorial. 
OL,18,FLiz Haigh-Reeve, who survived the      
OL,19,Fcrash, said it was "wonderful that     
OL,20,Fthere's going to be something here".   
